<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; } .header { background-color:
      #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 10px; text-align: center; } .content { padding: 20px; } .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; } .total
      { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #d9534f; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Konfirmasi Pesanan</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Halo, <strong>{{customerEmail}}</strong>!</p>
        <p>Terima kasih telah berbelanja di toko kami. Berikut detail pesanan Anda:</p>

        <table width="100%">
          <tr>
            <td>Order ID:</td>
            <td><strong>#{{orderId}}</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Tanggal:</td>
            <td>{{orderDate}}</td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <hr />

        <h3>Total Pembayaran:</h3>
        <p class="total">Rp {{totalAmount}}</p>

        <p>Mohon segera lakukan pembayaran sebelum kami mengirim barang Anda.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 My DDD App. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>